com.mozilla.secops

Class DetectNat

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mozilla.secops.DetectNat

  • public class DetectNat
extends Object
    Provides NAT detection transforms

    Currently this transform only operates on normalized Normalized.Type.HTTP_REQUEST events and is based on the detection of multiple user agents being identified for requests within the window for the same source IP address.

    The output from the transform is a PCollection of KV pairs where the key is a source IP address identified in the window and the value is a boolean set to true if there is a possibility the source address is a NAT gateway. If it is not suspected the source address is a NAT gateway, it will not be included in the output set.
